    <div class="overlay"> <!-- Overlay som vises ved hover -->
      <div class="text">Hoping to uncover a backup og GAIA, Aloy travels to the Forbidden West, where a mysterious and toxic blight is ravaging the environment, poisoning wildlife, and threatening the lives of those who dwell there. 
        She will meet new tribes in these unfamiliar lands and encounter ever deadlier machines.</div> <!-- Tekst i overlay -->
