    <div class="overlay"> <!-- Overlay som vises ved hover -->
      <div class="text">In Split Fiction, you and your co-op partner will become Mio and Zoe, two writers trapped in a simulation of their own imaginations after a high-tech attempt to steal their creative ideas goes badly wrong.</div> <!-- Tekst i overlay -->
