    <div class="overlay"> <!-- Overlay som vises ved hover -->
      <div class="text">Astro Bot is a 3D platformer in which the player controls a small robot, Astro Bot, with the DualSense controller. 
        Astro's move set is identical to his previous incarnations from Astro Bot Rescue Mission and Astro's Playroom, maintaining his ability to jump, hover, punch, and spin-attack.</div> <!-- Tekst i overlay -->
        <div class="text2">Game rating: 7+</div>
        <div class="text3">46GB Minimum</div>
        <div class="text4">1 player</div>
    </div> <!-- Slutt overlay -->
  </div> <!-- Slutt container -->

