    <div class="overlay"> <!-- Overlay som vises ved hover -->
      <div class="text">The incredible power of the symbiote forces Peter and Miles to face the ultimate test of strength, both inside and outside the mask, as they balance their lives, friendships and their duty to protect those in need.</div> <!-- Tekst i overlay -->
      <div class="text2">Game rating: 16+</div>
